## ACOUSTIC\_CONFIG\_RESOURCE\_URL variable

Name of the 'rel' attribute of a link element used to configure the delivery URL

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
ACOUSTIC_CONFIG_RESOURCE_URL = "wch-config-resource-url"
```
